Question: Many universities require that freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. In your opinion, is this a good or a bad thing? Explain your opinion on this issue.
Answer:
yes, i agree with this. for the first year, because students are not familiar with each other, if they all live on campus, it will be much easier for them to know each other. besides, in the first year, they may face some problems, if they live on campus, it will much easier to solve them.